and they won't say
what it's about.

298
00:15:00,807 --> 00:15:01,574
Hello?

299
00:15:01,688 --> 00:15:02,989
MAN:
Mrs. Dubois, this is

300
00:15:03,097 --> 00:15:04,677
All Right Carpet
Cleaning Service.

301
00:15:04,758 --> 00:15:05,701
I'm calling to offer you

302
00:15:05,781 --> 00:15:07,049
