ARIEL:
Bridget!

303
00:15:07,205 --> 00:15:08,077
Oops.

304
00:15:08,192 --> 00:15:09,765
This is the same exact day.

305
00:15:09,870 --> 00:15:11,203
Is that a yes?
JOE:
Ariel, here, take this.

306
00:15:11,339 --> 00:15:12,651
Because for $19.95 an hour,

307
00:15:12,746 --> 00:15:14,098
we can send a team
of professionals

308
00:15:14,163 --> 00:15:16,485
